    {
      "description": "Cassel warns that if Maret refuses or fails to appear, he will escalate the matter to a warrant for arrest, with all city guards notified. He implies that fleeing would only confirm the anomaly's threat. The tension in the tavern thickens.",
      "characters": ["Lucius Cassel", "Maret Halsey"],
      "kind": "action",
      "requiredPayoffs": []
